metadata.name: The Bernard D'sa Talk Show
metadata.description:
Bernard D’sa and Raindrops Atelier brings to you ‘The Bernard D’sa Talk Show’

Every episode has been designed to bring some added value to our lives, be it in the form of health, wealth management, being creative, and most importantly, helping you to stay motivated. Some finest entrepreneurs/creative folks and artists are ready to inspire you with their success stories with a walkthrough to the lessons they learned from their failures and created the path to success.

Exclusively featured on The Bernard D'sa Talk Show
